    "text": "This is a warning message displayed in a dialog. It informs the user about storage quota limitations for the product, with `{{productName}}` being the product name (e.g., ONLYOFFICE DocSpace) and `{{quotaLimits}}` listing the specific quota restrictions (e.g., \"10 GB\", \"5 users\").",
